    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<!-- WEREAD_SECTION_START --><!-- WEREAD_HIGHLIGHT_1_START --><div class="weread-card" data-position="1">  <span class="weread-text">师父不会答应让我为他报仇的……他只会说，阿越，不要报仇，不要学武，要好好活着。</span></div><!-- WEREAD_HIGHLIGHT_1_END --><!-- WEREAD_SECTION_END -->]]></content>
    
    
      
      
