  <entry>
    <title>第七章 绵针</title>
    <link href="https://californiafitzleo.github.io/2026/07/14/Book-14/07%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%83%E7%AB%A0%20%E7%BB%B5%E9%92%88/"/>
    <id>https://californiafitzleo.github.io/2026/07/14/Book-14/07%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%83%E7%AB%A0%20%E7%BB%B5%E9%92%88/</id>
    <published>2026-07-14T16:00:00.000Z</published>
    <updated>2026-07-22T13:27:03.585Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<!-- WEREAD_SECTION_START --><!-- WEREAD_HIGHLIGHT_1_START --><div class="weread-card" data-position="1">  <span class="weread-text">李舟吾道：“无论如何，他也不该死在裘铁鹤这等人手里。”却与七年前所说的话一样。</span></div><!-- WEREAD_HIGHLIGHT_1_END --><!-- WEREAD_HIGHLIGHT_2_START --><div class="weread-card" data-position="2">  <span class="weread-text">倘有一人在河边遇见一个溺水的孩童，此人忽发善念，入水将孩童救上岸，自己却脱力下沉，眼看便要淹死——袁姑娘，若你明知此人从前是个恶徒，是否会眼瞧此人淹死而不救？</span></div><!-- WEREAD_HIGHLIGHT_2_END --><!-- WEREAD_HIGHLIGHT_3_START --><div class="weread-card" data-position="3">  <span class="weread-text">侠之一字，是一念之仁、一时义愤，顾不全世间所有苦难不公。从前我若撞见他害人，自会杀他；如今他因善举而濒死，我自当相救；救活之后，他也当为从前恶行担责，我想常前辈到时自会给我一个交代。</span></div><!-- WEREAD_HIGHLIGHT_3_END --><!-- WEREAD_SECTION_END -->]]></content>
    
    
      
      
